<HEADLINE> Prince Charles Ends Uruguay Trip </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay (AP) -- Prince Charles wound up his trip to  
Uruguay by watching a soccer game and visiting a beach resort. 
</P>
<P>
	The Prince of Wales popped in for the first half of a soccer  
match Saturday at Centenario Stadium, then left midway through the 
match to head to Punta del Este, a popular Uruguayan beach resort 
